<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! We're gonna leave you behind!</font>

169
00:07:22,900 --> 00:07:25,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you up for bibimbap-ing or not?</font>

170
00:07:25,010 --> 00:07:27,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am, I am! I'm so up for bimbap-ing!</font>

171
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:39,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><b><font size="16"><font color="#fdff8f">Bibim-don</font></font></b></font></font>

172
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:39,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Arial"><font size="8"><b><font color="#816f6c">Meal ticket
Bibim style</font></b></font></font></font>

173
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:36,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wish we could've gotten the stone pot kind.</font>

174
00:07:33,770 --> 00:07:39,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="18"><font color="#ad2ebd"><b>Yup. This is good.</b></font></font></font></font>

175
00:07:36,670 --> 00:07:37,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?</font>

176
00:07:37,540 --> 00:07:38,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't beg for luxuries.</font>

177
00:07:37,640 --> 00:07:39,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="18"><font color="#199da7"><b>Either kind works...</b></font></font></font></font>

178
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:43,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sometimes, I get a little excited.</i></font>

179
00:07:40,980 --> 00:07:43,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><b><font size="20">{\an1}<font color="#383736">*Suzuki</font></font></b></font></font>

180
00:07:43,750 --> 00:07:44,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Like when...</i></font>

181
00:07:45,240 --> 00:07:50,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<font face="Arial Black"><font size="18"><font color="#efec8a">Popuri
<font color="#ea90e6">GRAND OPENING SALE
<font color="#dc3159">First 3 days only</font></font></font></font></font></font>

182
00:07:45,660 --> 00:07:48,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>a convenience store opens near my house.</i></font>

183
00:07:48,830 --> 00:07:50,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is today!</font>

184
00:07:50,550 --> 00:07:52,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm making a quick trip to the store!</font>

185
00:07:51,780 --> 00:07:53,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="12"><b>{\an4}<font color="#403635">I'm in the mood for ice cream
 after dinner this time of year
<font color="#d74201">-S</font></font></b></font></font></font>

186
00:07:53,670 --> 00:07:55,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, wait!</font>

187
00:07:55,760 --> 00:07:57,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will you buy some toilet paper for me?</font>

188
00:07:57,710 --> 00:08:00,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? That's cheaper at the supermarket.</font>

189
00:08:00,540 --> 00:08:03,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, we only have a third of a roll left.</font>

190
00:08:03,180 --> 00:08:04,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That is a problem.</font>

191
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:08,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, you're going out like that? 
So much for your pride as a woman.</font>

192
00:08:08,500 --> 00:08:09,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You need an exorcist?</font>

193
00:08:09,760 --> 00:08:12,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Arial"><font size="16"><b><font color="#a28577">Cigarettes</font></b></font></font></font>

194
00:08:09,970 --> 00:08:11,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Grab some Luckys for me.</font>

195
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:12,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not buying those!</font>

196
00:08:13,630 --> 00:08:18,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I mean, he did have a point. If you 
asked if I'd go see Tani-kun like this...</i></font>

197
00:08:18,580 --> 00:08:19,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>that'd be a hard no.</i></font>

198
00:08:19,980 --> 00:08:21,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="30"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#f5fca7">Popuri</font></font></font></font>

199
00:08:23,150 --> 00:08:23,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, hey.</font>

200
00:08:24,540 --> 00:08:25,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

201
00:08:26,490 --> 00:08:28,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font size="18"><font color="#ccffaa"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b>We had the
 same thought</b></font></font></font></font>

202
00:08:27,410 --> 00:08:29,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For real? What kind of coincidence is this?</font>

203
00:08:29,340 --> 00:08:30,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you bring the flier and coupons?</font>

204
00:08:30,960 --> 00:08:32,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You bet I did!</font>

205
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:34,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, those gym shorts
are from middle school.</font>

206
00:08:34,500 --> 00:08:36,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't wear those out of the house.</font>

207
00:08:36,280 --> 00:08:40,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about your fancy 
pretend-loungewear-for-going-out track pants?</font>

208
00:08:40,060 --> 00:08:41,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should quit while you're ahead.</font>

209
00:08:41,530 --> 00:08:42,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, shut up.</font>

210
00:08:47,260 --> 00:08:49,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! Taira's working here!</font>

211
00:08:49,230 --> 00:08:51,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't show up all excited on our first day.</font>

212
00:08:51,220 --> 00:08:52,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know I would.</font>

213
00:08:52,520 --> 00:08:54,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Say, Taira, you don't live
around here, do you?</font>

214
00:08:54,630 --> 00:08:57,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Somewhere near school
 is easier on weekdays, y'know?</font>

215
00:08:57,630 --> 00:09:00,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Plus, I'd see everyone from
middle school near my house.</font>

216
00:09:00,020 --> 00:09:02,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? What's wrong with having
your friends come see you at work?</font>

217
00:09:05,770 --> 00:09:07,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As you may inconvenience other customers,</font>

218
00:09:07,880 --> 00:09:10,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">could I ask you to hurry up
 with your shopping and leave?</font>

219
00:09:10,470 --> 00:09:12,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And suddenly he's got his work face on.</font>

220
00:09:13,880 --> 00:09:15,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Somehow...</font>

221
00:09:14,030 --> 00:09:23,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an6}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font size="30"><font color="#432577">Ummm...</font></font></b></font></font>

222
00:09:15,060 --> 00:09:19,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">having a guy my own age working the register 
makes it embarrassing to buy toilet paper.</font>

223
00:09:19,660 --> 00:09:21,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've got more to be embarrassed about.</font>

224
00:09:21,440 --> 00:09:23,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I could not care less about your embarrassment.</font>

225
00:09:23,540 --> 00:09:25,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See you later!</font>

226
00:09:25,070 --> 00:09:27,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll come to print tickets and pick up
stuff shipped from flea markets!</font>

227
00:09:27,980 --> 00:09:29,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't increase my workload!</font>

228
00:09:35,510 --> 00:09:37,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gapacho's recommendation is good.</font>

229
00:09:37,100 --> 00:09:38,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not bad, Gapacho.</font>

230
00:09:41,610 --> 00:09:43,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did it rain today?</font>

231
00:09:43,880 --> 00:09:47,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe for a second this evening? 
It stopped right away, though.</font>

232
00:09:47,420 --> 00:09:48,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah? I thought so.</font>

233
00:09:50,710 --> 00:09:53,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You get this nice smell after it rains.</font>

234
00:09:56,330 --> 00:09:58,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry. I dunno what you mean.</font>

235
00:09:58,210 --> 00:10:01,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, it's like plants and the earth...</font>

236
00:10:02,130 --> 00:10:04,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry. Please just forget it.</font>

237
00:10:08,680 --> 00:10:10,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A Cub motorcycle shifting gears?
 Is it the police?</font>

238
00:10:10,940 --> 00:10:11,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

239
00:10:13,470 --> 00:10:15,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're coming this way!</font>

240
00:10:15,050 --> 00:10:16,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Make a break for it! Run!</font>

241
00:10:19,100 --> 00:10:20,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

242
00:10:20,970 --> 00:10:22,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nabe!</font>

243
00:10:22,760 --> 00:10:24,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? What're you doing here?</font>

244
00:10:24,610 --> 00:10:26,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was out on my bike and took a detour.</font>

245
00:10:26,780 --> 00:10:29,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You get a nice wind on this road here.</font>

246
00:10:29,590 --> 00:10:31,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The one most likely to get 
nabbed by the cops is here.</font>

247
00:10:32,550 --> 00:10:36,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought, "Ugh. There's a delinquent 
couple hanging out here. This is the pits."</font>

248
00:10:36,950 --> 00:10:38,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad it was just you two, 
Suzuki and Yamada.</font>

249
00:10:38,970 --> 00:10:41,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My friend saw me and thought, 
"This is the pits."</font>

250
00:10:41,370 --> 00:10:44,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, Suzuki, it takes guts 
to go out like that, doesn't it?</font>

251
00:10:44,560 --> 00:10:46,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? This is my neighborhood,
so it's fine, right?</font>

252
00:10:46,700 --> 00:10:48,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Middle school gym shorts are a bad sign.</font>

253
00:10:48,980 --> 00:10:51,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder what Tani-kun 
would think if he saw this.</font>

254
00:10:51,810 --> 00:10:54,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Not happening! 
I'd never let him see me like this.</font>

255
00:10:54,780 --> 00:10:56,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not <i>that</i> different from your usual.</font>

256
00:10:56,570 --> 00:10:57,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It most certainly is!</font>

257
00:10:58,050 --> 00:11:00,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I've got nothing to worry about.</font>

258
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:03,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tani-kun would never go out to the
convenience store at this time of night.</font>

259
00:11:11,020 --> 00:11:13,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Suzuki-san?</font>

260
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:18,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And... Yamada-kun and Watanabe-san, too.</font>

261
00:11:18,320 --> 00:11:20,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><b><font size="14">{\an7}<font color="#78e2e7">You noticed</font></font></b></font></font>

262
00:11:18,590 --> 00:11:19,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Too slow.</font>

263
00:11:23,790 --> 00:11:26,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tani! Why are you wandering 
around at this time of night?</font>

264
00:11:26,500 --> 00:11:28,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You must be a hoodlum! A hoodlum!</font>

265
00:11:28,090 --> 00:11:30,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't close your eyes to your own faults.</font>

266
00:11:28,220 --> 00:11:30,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Arial"><b><font size="18"><font color="#49cbbd">Heading home from cram school...</font></font></b></font></font>

267
00:11:31,130 --> 00:11:33,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why did Suzuki-san disappear?</font>

268
00:11:33,300 --> 00:11:35,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well... don't let it bother you.</font>

269
00:11:35,220 --> 00:11:36,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just go and finish your shopping.</font>

270
00:11:36,890 --> 00:11:39,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Suzuki was never here.</font>

271
00:11:39,180 --> 00:11:40,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

272
00:11:45,280 --> 00:11:47,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You must have <i>something</i> to say.</font>

273
00:11:45,350 --> 00:11:48,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="14"><b>{\an7}<font color="#3d383a">Not getting teased leads 
to its own kind of anxiety</font></b></font></font></font>

274
00:11:48,060 --> 00:11:50,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay! Run while you have the chance!</font>

275
00:11:50,220 --> 00:11:52,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And make sure you explain yourself later, okay?</font>

276
00:11:52,570 --> 00:11:53,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you both.</font>

277
00:11:54,260 --> 00:11:56,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! Gimme my helmet back!</font>

278
00:11:57,880 --> 00:11:59,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm sorry, Tani-kun!</i></font>

279
00:11:59,430 --> 00:12:01,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to be myself with you,</i></font>

280
00:12:01,480 --> 00:12:05,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but that doesn't mean I can
 show you every little thing!</i></font>

281
00:12:05,330 --> 00:12:08,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If I did and it disillusioned you...</i></font>

282
00:12:08,380 --> 00:12:10,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't want that!</i></font>

283
00:12:14,270 --> 00:12:18,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Okay! Now that I've run this far, 
like Achilles and the tortoise...</i></font>

284
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:19,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Suzuki-san.</font>

285
00:12:20,510 --> 00:12:22,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-Achilles...</font>

286
00:12:24,910 --> 00:12:26,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you running away?</font>

287
00:12:27,890 --> 00:12:30,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">B-Because...</font>

288
00:12:33,530 --> 00:12:36,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But none of that bothers me.</font>

289
00:12:36,940 --> 00:12:40,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if it doesn't seem like it's 
a big deal from your perspective,</font>

290
00:12:40,700 --> 00:12:43,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it's a vibes problem for me.</font>

291
00:12:43,750 --> 00:12:45,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vibes?</font>

292
00:12:49,770 --> 00:12:51,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even though you don't care with Yamada-kun?</font>

293
00:12:51,750 --> 00:12:52,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

294
00:12:56,630 --> 00:12:58,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I mean, he's just Yamada.</font>

295
00:12:58,800 --> 00:13:01,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've known him since middle school, 
so this is kind of small potatoes.</font>

296
00:13:01,970 --> 00:13:03,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about Taira-kun and Watanabe-san?</font>

297
00:13:03,860 --> 00:13:07,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Nabe and I have been together 
since our first year of high school,</font>

298
00:13:07,500 --> 00:13:09,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and Taira is... Well, he's Taira.</font>

299
00:13:08,640 --> 00:13:09,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Arial"><font size="14"><b><font color="#304670">Dismissed</font></b></font></font></font>

300
00:13:10,350 --> 00:13:11,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

301
00:13:12,310 --> 00:13:14,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><b>{\an9}<font color="#f6e065">Huh?</font></b></font></font>

302
00:13:14,150 --> 00:13:17,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tani-kun, you seem blatantly upset right now.</font>

303
00:13:16,150 --> 00:13:20,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="20"><b>{\an8}<font color="#e4839a">I'm understanding more and more...</font></b></font></font></font>

304
00:13:17,920 --> 00:13:20,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't hear it from 
someone who blatantly ran.</font>

305
00:13:20,110 --> 00:13:21,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, boldly spoken.</font>

306
00:13:21,990 --> 00:13:22,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just...</font>

307
00:13:23,330 --> 00:13:28,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm jealous of how long Yamada-kun
 and the others have known you.</font>

308
00:13:31,950 --> 00:13:32,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tani-kun...</font>

309
00:13:33,800 --> 00:13:36,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Imagine there's some food here.</font>

310
00:13:36,670 --> 00:13:40,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, let's say we have a slapped-together
 dish on a random plate</font>

311
00:13:40,300 --> 00:13:43,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and a nicely presented one on a cute plate.</font>

312
00:13:43,990 --> 00:13:49,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if they both taste the same, 
Tani-kun, I want to give you the nice one.</font>

313
00:13:49,940 --> 00:13:52,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to show myself off! 
Basically, that's it!</font>

314
00:13:55,580 --> 00:13:57,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter how it's presented,</font>

315
00:13:57,750 --> 00:14:00,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">if it's a dish I like, then I'm not 
concerned about the rest.</font>

316
00:14:03,820 --> 00:14:06,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Arial Black"><font size="36"><font color="#f9ff9b">Huh?</font></font></font></font>

317
00:14:04,730 --> 00:14:06,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, that's problematic.</font>

318
00:14:05,200 --> 00:14:06,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#f9ff9b">Hang on...</font></font></font>

319
00:14:06,950 --> 00:14:07,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

320
00:14:07,950 --> 00:14:10,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I've got a pretty dish on a pretty plate,</font>

321
00:14:10,680 --> 00:14:15,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">hearing stuff like "I like how this looks" or
 "this plating is nice" get me pumped up.</font>

322
00:14:15,540 --> 00:14:16,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pumped up?</font>

323
00:14:17,930 --> 00:14:18,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean the vibes?</font>

324
00:14:20,190 --> 00:14:22,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, the vibes!</font>

325
00:14:25,290 --> 00:14:26,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tani-kun.</font>

326
00:14:26,370 --> 00:14:27,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me ride on the back.</font>

327
00:14:27,960 --> 00:14:29,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

328
00:14:29,100 --> 00:14:30,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I might not be very good at this.</font>

329
00:14:30,820 --> 00:14:32,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine! Don't worry!</font>

